data.description: This meticulously cared-for ranch home is ready for its new owners, offering a range of recent upgrades, including a new furnace and A/C installed in 2021, as well as a water heater added in 2023. The outdoor space is adorned with thriving berry bushes, grapevines, garden beds, and fresh patio stones, creating a welcoming atmosphere.  Inside, the home features an open floor plan that enhances the updated bathroom, refreshed flooring throughout, and a modern kitchen with granite countertops. Its strategic location places it just minutes away from I-88 and the Outlet Mall, ensuring easy access to both daily conveniences and leisure activities.  Notably, the garage has been transformed into a comfortable lounge area, though it can be effortlessly reverted to its original function if desired. Don't miss the opportunity to explore this charming property; schedule a tour today to envision your new chapter in this well-maintained ranch home.
